---

<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Seite nicht gefunden — Open Data Enabled AI</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.png" type="image/png" />
    <script>
        (function () {
            var path = window.location.pathname
            if (path.indexOf('/docs/') === 0 || path === '/docs') {
                var newPath = path.replace('/docs', '') || '/'
                window.location.replace(newPath)
            }
        })()
    </script>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: #0d1117;
            color: #e6edf3;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 540px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #58a6ff;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #8b949e;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        p {
            color: #8b949e;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .links {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
            background: #21262d;
            color: #58a6ff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        a:hover {
            background: #30363d;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Seite nicht gefunden</h2>
        <p>Die angeforderte Seite existiert nicht oder wurde verschoben. Vielleicht findest du hier, was du suchst:</p>
        <div class="links">
            <a href="/">Startseite</a>
            <a href="/de/about/">Ueber das Projekt</a>
            <a href="/de/roadmap/">Roadmap</a>
            <a href="/de/community/">Community</a>
            <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
